title: Top Floor Corner Apt with **$1000 Off  Rent** at Grand & Syndicate
posting_body: ['Property Address', '35 Syndicate St S - 403 | St. Paul, MN 55105', 'Available: Now!', 'Offered By', 'At Home Apartments |', 'show contact info', 'Description', 'Top Floor Corner Apt at Grand & Syndicate with $1000 Off First Months Rent!', 'Apartment 403 is a top floor home with north and east-facing windows which provide a nice view and plenty of morning sunshine.', 'The elegant F floor design features a private deck.', 'A walk-in closet in the master bedroom, in-home washer/dryer, and two entryway closest are just part of what makes this plush home so impressive.', 'A Contemporary Landmark in a Celebrated Location.', 'Grand & Syndicate is a mixed-use building on the corner of Grand Avenue and Syndicate Street in Saint Paul.', 'The new four-story structure includes underground parking, office space, the home office for At Home Apartments, and 26 upscale apartment homes.', 'Call us at', 'show contact info', 'or visit us at <URL> for more information and tour options.', 'Photos are a representation of the property and may not be of the exact apartment.', '**$150 Administration Fee added to lease.', 'Pet fees/restrictions may apply.', 'Please inquire about your specific pet.', '**', 'Amenities', 'Keyless Entry', 'Washer/Dryer in Apt', 'Granite Countertop', "9' Ceilings", 'Rooftop Lounge & Patio', 'Heated Underground Parking', 'Elevator', 'Stainless Steel Appliances', 'Vinyl Tile Plank Flooring', 'Online Rent Payment Portal', '24-hour Emergency Maintenance', 'Smoke-Free Living', 'Management Office on-site', 'Year Built: 2018', 'Details', 'Beds/Baths: 1BD/1.0BA', 'Square Feet: 750', 'Rental Terms', 'Rent: $1,849.00', 'Available: Now!', 'Application Fee: $55.00', 'Security Deposit: $600.00', 'Pet Policy', 'Cats allowed', 'Dogs not allowed']
